comments: She was great! Met her in her office one day to "adjust" my grade. She was a good teacher in all areas! I would definitely take her again. Thank you Gayla!

Very easy teacher. She does everything short of filling out the scantron for you. If you are looking to actually learn the material instead of just regurgitating facts, however, take someone else. All she tells students is what will be on the test and nothing more. She is funny and very friendly.

Does not know class material and cannot manage a class. She is an easy teacher, but you will not learn anything coz she is never prepared. If you want to get a proper career, I suggest you take another professor.

she is super nice and easy as long as you do your work she doesn\'t care she keeps you mayb forty minutes of the class time and she gives you the answers to her tests the day before the test date very very nice lady i would recommend her
